<title>HUNGARY: Zalakeramia reports rising profits for Q1.</title>
<headline>Zalakeramia reports rising profits for Q1.</headline>
<dateline>BUDAPEST 1997-05-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>Three-month period ending March 31, 1997.</p>
<p>(Figures in millions of forints unless stated)</p>
<p>					  Jan-March 1997   Jan-March 1996</p>
<p>    Operating profit		   156.3	vs     114.3</p>
<p>    Pre-tax profit		     159.8	vs     119.8</p>
<p>    Net profit			   144.2	vs     105.4</p>
<p>    Sales revenue		    1,028.8	vs     743.9</p>
<p>    Costs of sales		     657.2	vs     485.7</p>
<p>    Gross margin			 371.5	vs     258.2</p>
<p>    Selling, gen. and admin costs  195.5	vs     176.5</p>
<p>    Other operating revenue	   36.8	vs	85.2</p>
<p>    Other operating expenditure     56.6	vs	52.6</p>
<p>    Interest revenue		    26.0	vs	15.6</p>
<p>    Interest expenditure		22.5	vs	10.1</p>
<p>    Taxation				15.6	vs	14.4</p>
<p>NOTE - Zalakeramia Rt is a tile manufacturer. The figures are not audited and they were calculated in accordance with International Accounting Standards.</p>
<p>-- Budapest newsroom +36 1 327-4040</p>
